				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>This assignment was an in class competition, and the winner would have their idea turned into a collaborative project over the summer. Technically our pitch recieved second place, but it was more or less the AR portion of our game that was actually used for the project. I did not participate in the actual development of this project, to be clear.</p><p>More Info:</p><p><a href="https://artunews.com/2018/10/27/adventure-bay-brings-gaming-to-children-with-cerebral-palsy/">Academy Of Art News</a></p><p><a href="https://sgoodale1.wixsite.com/adventurebay">Project Website</a></p><p> </p>					</div>
