					<description><![CDATA[For this project, we were asked to prototype a game comissioned by the Kroc Center in San Francisco. The Kroc Center was looking for a game of some kind which would prompt youths to engage with their physical community more and partake in the betterment of it too. We came up with a simple game ...]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="693" class="elementor elementor-693 elementor-bc-flex-widget" data-elementor-settings="[]">
						<div class="elementor-inner">
							<div class="elementor-section-wrap">
							<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-e738db7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="e738db7" data-element_type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
							<div class="elementor-row">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-056e4cd" data-id="056e4cd" data-element_type="column">
			<div class="elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated">
							<div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b30c88a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="b30c88a" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>For this project, we were asked to prototype a game comissioned by the Kroc Center in San Francisco. The Kroc Center was looking for a game of some kind which would prompt youths to engage with their physical community more and partake in the betterment of it too.</p><p>We came up with a simple game that would teach players the fundamentals of proper waste disposal, as well as how to confront problems related to improper waste disposal in their community.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e764ad9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html" data-id="e764ad9" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="html.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<style>.embed-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 59.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; } .embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container embed { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }</style><div class='embed-container'><iframe src='https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/e/2PACX-1vS3CEKkfFEZnrODeRQhs4HHyynxu0Lt5ShASJbC_pNgjIG8dhs19ww_gVUZva5Y8RwrojsGNfvM2Wud/embed?start=false&loop=false&delayms=60000' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen='true' mozallowfullscreen='true' webkitallowfullscreen='true'></iframe></div>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9d77ee1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="9d77ee1" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>The class this was for ran each project as a competition, and unfortunately this pitch did not win first place, but instead took second in the class.</p><p>The first place winner&#8217;s pitch was sort of a building dress up type of game. The idea was to encourage children to partake in community service. There isn&#8217;t much gameplay, and it&#8217;s not too exciting, but I imagine smaller kids would find some joy in this type of game.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d48ea9e elementor-aspect-ratio-169 elementor-widget elementor-widget-video" data-id="d48ea9e" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/youtu.be\/gJHz77c7iAY&quot;,&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;aspect_ratio&quot;:&quot;169&quot;}" data-widget_type="video.default">
