				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-362f2289 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="362f2289" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>This game was made for a class focused on rapid prototyping. The prompt for this particular project was to make a top-down shooter style game, but there had to be some kind of &#8220;twist&#8221; to it. This twist could be tweaking the genre, or having an unexpected story twist.</p><p>I was already working on studying and <a style="background-color: #ffffff;" href="./../../../portfolio/notline-miami/index.html">replicating <em>Hotline Miami</em></a>, so I wanted to take this particular project in a different direction.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
						</div>
					</div>
		</div>
				<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-296ec533" data-id="296ec533" data-element_type="column">
			<div class="elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated">
							<div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a19f21e elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon" data-id="a19f21e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="icon.default">
